      <h1 class="font-bold text-5xl font-header uppercase pt-10 text-center">Accelerated Pilot Training</h1>
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl italic pt-5 pb-3 px-10 lg:max-w-lg text-center">Full time pilot training to get your certificate and ratings done as quick as possible</h2>
      <p class="p-text w-3/4 pb-5">
        SimpliFly makes becoming a pilot simple.  SimpliFly's accelerated pilot programs are designed specifically for individuals like you who are eager to take to the skies and accelerate their training journey.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col px-5 gap-3 pb-5">
        <div class="flex flex-row ">
          <div class="text-sky-500 pr-2 font-extrabold">✈</div>
          <h3 class="lg:px-10 pl-4 p-text text-left">Intensive focus, rapid progress</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row ">
          <div class="text-sky-500 pr-2 font-extrabold">✈</div>
          <h3 class="lg:px-10 pl-4 p-text text-left">Experienced instructors, exceptional guidance</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row ">
          <div class="text-sky-500 pr-2 font-extrabold">✈</div>
          <h3 class="lg:px-10 pl-4 p-text text-left">Efficient progression, optimal results</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row ">
          <div class="text-sky-500 pr-2 font-extrabold">✈</div>
          <h3 class="lg:px-10 pl-4 p-text text-left">Your pathway to an aviation career</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <%= link_to "ENROLL TODAY", enroll_path,  target: "blank", data: { turbo: false }, class: "btn-primary mt-3 mb-10" %>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/2">
      <div class="lg:px-10">
        <%= image_tag "ally-cfi.webp", alt: "SimpliFly CFI", class: "object-contain lg:rounded-2xl"%>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="flex flex-col items-center pb-10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl flex flex-col pt-10 px-5">
    <h3 class="text-5xl font-header uppercase font-semibold">How It Works</h3>
    <h4 class="text-3xl text-slate-600 italic py-5">Find out how to enroll in our accelerated program</h4>
    <p class="text-lg">The first thing we recommend is to do a discovery flight. Your discovery flight is designed to give you a taste of what it's like to be a pilot. You'll spend approximately 60 minutes in the air with one of our certified flight instructors, who will guide you through the basics of flying and answer any questions you may have. You'll also have the opportunity to take the controls and experience the thrill of flying first hand.</p>
    <div class="pt-10 flex">
      <%= link_to "BOOK DISCOVERY FLIGHT", discovery_flight_path,  target: "blank", data: { turbo: false }, class: "btn-primary my-3" %>
    </div>
    
    <h3 class="text-5xl font-header uppercase font-semibold pt-20">After the Discovery Flight</h3>
    <h4 class="text-3xl text-slate-600 italic py-5">Enroll at SimpliFly and start training</h4>
    <p class="text-lg">Our team will pair you with a certified flight instructor (CFI) who will work with you to create a personalized plan with your goals in mind. You will train full time and work on getting your pilot certificate and ratings.  Below are the certificate and ratings you can expect to receive upon successful completion of our accelerated pilot training program.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<%= render "shared/pilot_programs"%>

<section class="bg-gradient-to-t lg:bg-gradient-to-l from-sky-800 to-slate-900 text-white">
